title: The Outer Limits - The Uncensored Collection
description:
Fans of the 1990s "new" Outer Limits may be aware than some of the 
episodes featured some great female nudity.

Unfortunately these episodes have been widely censored both in
the DVD releases (the Canadian ones) and in some TV broadcasts.

Here then is a collection of nine such stories, presented in
their intended form, with nipples and some pubes on display.

Do not adjust your television...

The episodes are:-

S01E02 - Valerie 23
S01E14 - A New Breed
S01E16 - Caught in the Act
S03E01 - Bits of Love
S03E13 - Double Helix
S04E15 - Mary 25
S04E17 - Lithia
S04E23 - The Origin of Species
S05E07 - The Human Operators


The episodes "Lithia" and "Mary 25" were created for this collection
by DVD footage to the uncensored TV broadcast version (see the
shower scene in "Lithia" for example. The TV footage is somewhat lower
quality than the rest of the episode, but it's not long, especially in
the case of the "Mary 25" breasts revealed portion.

The short sample video and image are from "Double Helix".

The episodes are encoded as mp4, at 720 x 540 pixels, 23.976 fps, 128k aac stereo sound. The videos are encoded at an average of 2000kbps.
